Text: Vacation CoverageHave a look at the shift schedule please and see if you could possible work for me November th Daylights Saturday Thankyou Bart

GALLUP STATION is absolute low on surge margin for this unit IF IT GOES BELOW RAISE THE SUCTION SET POINT The unit will lock into minimum RPM when surge margin hits and will not unlock until surge margin gets above Recommended to change set point in increments when lowering set point so surge margin can be better monitored Alarm limits have changed LO LO LO Thanks Bart

FW Chatfield Compressor StationExtended forecast for the Tuesday highs lows Gave Phil the go a head for his outage Spoke with Jim Merrick on the Owatonna team to inform him of this outage He informed me that the units breaker is lockedout and if the unit is needed a callout will have to be made Thanks Bart Original Message From Monden Bart Sent Wednesday January AM To DLETS Gas Controllers Graves Jerry Subject Chatfield Compressor Station Received a call from Peoples Coop Service today and spoke with Phil Swenson He informed me that there will be an outage of electrical power to Chatfield Compressor Station on to Phil would like to receive a call back to proceed with the outage so he can schedule it with the electric suppler Thanks Bart
